Lisa's got a new life as a flight
attendant for Virgin Atlantic.

1304
01:32:52,319 --> 01:32:54,513
I hear she's got herself a new fella.

1305
01:32:56,318 --> 01:33:00,027
As for me, I fought unsuccessfully
against extradition...

1306
01:33:00,118 --> 01:33:05,111
...from Frankfurt to Singapore on charges
of fraud, forgery and breach of trust.

1307
01:33:07,237 --> 01:33:10,229
I was sentenced to six and
a half years in prison.

1308
01:33:11,117 --> 01:33:14,711
Despite rumours of secret bank
accounts and hidden millions,...

1309
